caller_intent: The caller, Diane Conrad, attempted to reach Corbin but was informed he was unavailable and opted to leave a voicemail instead.
resolution_steps: Agent informed caller Corbin was on the phone.
Offered to send call to voicemail or connect to another agent.
Caller declined assistance and requested voicemail option.
Agent confirmed voicemail request and paused call.
summary: Caller Diane Conrad attempted to reach Corbin but was informed he was unavailable. She agreed to leave a voicemail message for him. The agent facilitated the voicemail transfer and ended the call.
